data.description: Incredible opportunity. Turn this fixer into something great and bring back the old charm. Box beam ceilings, custom built in cabinet, wood floors, large basement, many features of the 1900s. Lot is over sized and features a detached garage with room for more parking behind gate. Property being sold As-Is, but so many possibilities with this one. Priced to Sell Fast, See it today!
